  	<h2 class='quiz__subtitle'>Which quality do you admire the most in a friend?</h2>
    
    <div class='quiz__inner-container second-container'>
      
      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q2' data-next='q3' data-answer='a'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>They know how to rescue you from an uncomfortable situation</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q2' data-next='q3' data-answer='b'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>They always show up for you and put up with your antics</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q2' data-next='q3' data-answer='c'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>They are incredibly resourceful</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q2' data-next='q3' data-answer='d'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>They value you exactly for who you are, flaws included</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q2' data-next='q3' data-answer='e'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>They come to you for advice, because they know how intelligent and deep you are</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div> 
  
