      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q5' data-next='last' data-answer='b'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>When you have amazing friends, no problem is too big.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q5' data-next='last' data-answer='c'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>Where are we going and how extravagant a wardrobe should I pack?</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q5' data-next='last' data-answer='d'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>You know I’m always up for a challenge.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q5' data-next='last' data-answer='e'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
