        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q5' data-next='last' data-answer='f'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>I am so over this damsel in distress nonsense.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q5' data-next='last' data-answer='g'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>People do crazy things... when they're in love.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q5' data-next='last' data-answer='h'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>What a joy to think of all we'll have in common. We'll have conversations worth having.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q5' data-next='last' data-answer='i'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>I see a darkness in you, and in that darkness, eyes staring back at me.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='quiz__option' data-type='answer' data-current='q5' data-next='last' data-answer='j'>
        <div class='quiz__txt-container'>
          <h3>And now, we will grow together.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    
